419 ControlTableItemInfo_t DYNAMIXEL::getControlTableItemInfo(uint16_t model_num, uint8_t control_item)
420 {
421  uint8_t item_idx, i = 0;
422  const ModelControlTableInfo_t *p_common_ctable = nullptr;
423  const ModelControlTableInfo_t *p_dep_ctable = nullptr;
424  ControlTableItemInfo_t item_info;
425  memset(&item_info, 0, sizeof(item_info));
426 
427  switch(model_num)
428  {
429  case AX12A:
430  case AX12W:
431  case AX18A:
432  case DX113:
433  case DX116:
434  case DX117:
435  case RX10:
436  case RX24F:
437  case RX28:
438  case RX64:
439  p_common_ctable = control_table_1_0;
440  break;
441 
442  case EX106:
443  p_common_ctable = control_table_1_0;
444  p_dep_ctable = ex_control_table;
445  break;
446 
447  case MX12W:
448  case MX28:
449  p_common_ctable = control_table_1_1;
450  break;
451 
452  case MX64:
453  p_common_ctable = control_table_1_1;
454  p_dep_ctable = mx64_control_table;
455  break;
456 
457  case MX106:
458  p_common_ctable = control_table_1_1;
459  p_dep_ctable = mx106_control_table;
460  break;
461 
462  case MX28_2:
463  p_common_ctable = control_table_2_0;
464  p_dep_ctable = mx28_2_control_table;
465  break;
466 
467  case MX64_2:
468  case MX106_2:
469  p_common_ctable = control_table_2_0;
470  p_dep_ctable = mx64_106_2_control_table;
471  break;
472 
473  case XL320:
474  p_common_ctable = xl320_control_table;
475  break;
476 
477  case XC430_W150:
478  case XC430_W240:
479  case XL430_W250:
480  case XXL430_W250:
481  case XXC430_W250:
482  p_common_ctable = control_table_2_0;
483  p_dep_ctable = xc430_xl430_control_table;
484  break;
485 
486  case XL330_M288:
487  case XL330_M077:
488  case XC330_M181:
489  case XC330_M288:
